### GET HTTP Request

`GET https://ept.praavahealth.com/API/PatientPortal/Offers?token=<token>&upi=<upi>`

### Request Information

| Category          | Value                                                                           |
| ---------         | ---------------------------------------------------------------                 |
| HTTP Request      | GET                                                                             |
| URL               | https://ept.praavahealth.com/API/PatientPortal/Offers?token=<token>&upi=<upi>     | 

### Headers
No Headers required

### Input Schema of request

| Parameter  | Description                                                     | Required |
| ---------  | --------------------------------------------------------------- | -------- |
| token      | Mandatory token for authorization.                              | true     |
| upi        | UPI of the individual patient.                                  | true     |     

### Output Schema of request

| Filed          | Description                                                     |
| ---------      | --------------------------------------------------------------- |
| success        | status of the request.                                          |
| result         | json array of all the special discounts.                                  |    
| message        | message of the response .                                        |    